						</dl>
						<figure class="thumb tright show-info-icon" style="width: 256px"> 	<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210512083934/https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/essentialsdocs/images/1/1b/EggSummary.png/revision/latest?cb=20190218181518" class="image"><img alt="" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20210512083934im_/https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/essentialsdocs/images/1/1b/EggSummary.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/256?cb=20190218181518" decoding="async" width="256" height="192" class="thumbimage" data-image-name="EggSummary.png" data-image-key="EggSummary.png"></a> 	 	<figcaption class="thumbcaption"> 		 			<a href="/web/20210512083934/https://essentialsdocs.fandom.com/wiki/File:EggSummary.png" class="info-icon"><svg><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-info-small"></use></svg></a> 		 		 		 			<p class="caption">The <a href="/web/20210512083934/https://essentialsdocs.fandom.com/wiki/Summary_screens" title="Summary screens">summary screen</a> for a Pokémon egg</p> 		 	</figcaption> </figure>
